      "name": "transcript",
      "description": "Training transcript records table tracking user enrollments, completion status, assignment dates, due dates, completion dates, training progress, and compliance training completion data. Purpose: Core transaction table for training enrollment and completion tracking, essential for compliance training completion analysis, overdue training identification, and training progress monitoring. Contains enrollment records linking users to training activities with status, dates, and completion metrics. Used in queries to count users who completed mandatory compliance training, to identify employees with overdue training (due date passed and not completed), to calculate training completion rates, to track training progress and engagement, and to analyze training effectiveness. Joins with users for employee information, with activities for course details, and serves as the primary table for all training completion and enrollment queries.",
      "tableReference": {
        "table": "transcript"
